originalText.text:
One of the Best SMM experts there!
Hello,
I have been using a lot of social media marketing panels for the last 5 years, I am the CEO of the SMM agency in Qatar, there more than 80% of positive feelings and the huge pleasure of collaborating with the SMM-Heaven.net site, their support is decent, professional and really damn quick.
I have been working with them for the last 6 months, switched from the other main 3 suppliers ( would like to avoid revealing their names ). Yes heaven's prices could be 8-12% higher than other big ones, yes they have fulfilled may be less orders, but not the volume that should be counted by the client, but the quality.
If my client is satisfied, i am satisfied as well.
I am not trying to promote, but just can advise to try and decide.

Best wishes, good luck in the future, work on improvements and 4* would definitely turn into 5*

sincerely your's Andrew D.
